videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond puts a little too much heat on a pitch to Trayveon Williams as the Aggies turn it over deep in their own territory.
videos.headline: Auburn recovers fumble deep in Texas A&M territory

videos.description: Auburn cashes in on some trickery as WR Ryan Davis collects a backwards pass and slingshots a 20-yard touchdown to a wide-open Sal Cannella.
videos.headline: Auburn reaches into bag of tricks for 20-yard TD pass

videos.description: Auburn's defense lays out a red carpet for Aggies RB Trayveon Williams, who strikes the open hole and motors untouched to the end zone for a 38-yard TD.
videos.headline: Williams busts loose for 38-yard TD

videos.description: Texas A&M RB Trayveon Williams snatches a one-handed screen pass, sheds multiple tackles and muscles his way into the end zone for a 14-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Williams snags 1-handed pass, powers in for 14-yard TD

videos.description: Trayveon Williams mashes in his second rushing touchdown, and third total TD of the game, on a 1-yard score.
videos.headline: Williams scores 3rd TD of the day for Texas A&M

videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond attempts a long throw to the sideline and is picked off by Noah Ignioghene.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's scoring threat stalls with INT

videos.description: Auburn's Jarrett Stidham lofts a perfect throw to the pylon as Darius Slayton leaps and snatches the ball out of the air, setting up a 1-yard punch-in for Chandler Cox.
videos.headline: Slayton's beautiful catch sets up 1-yard Auburn TD

videos.description: With less than 2 minutes to play, Auburn takes a 28-24 lead on Texas A&M as Jarrett Stidham slings a pretty end zone throw to Seth Williams, who extends and secures the 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Stidham hits Williams on a dime to take late lead

videos.description: Seth Williams hauls in an 11-yard TD pass from Jarrett Stidham with 1:41 left to complete Auburn's rally to beat No. 20 Texas A&M 28-24.
